---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Erro do servidor" description="Algo deu errado." noindex>
  <section class="container-page py-20 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-danger uppercase tracking-wider">Erro 500</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-ink">A linha embolou.</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto text-ink-muted text-lg">
      Algo deu errado do nosso lado. Tenta de novo daqui a pouco. Se o problema persistir, fala com a gente.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/">Voltar pra Home</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="/contato">Falar com o suporte</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
